---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Nicholas Charriere" showHome={false}>
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold my-8">Nicholas Charriere</h1>
  <p class="max-w-xl">
    Engineer with a passion for creating things. Currently building{" "}
    <a
      class="text-text-700 font-medium underline hover:text-froly-500 transition-all duration-200 hover:no-underline underline-offset-2"
      href="https://axflow.dev">Axflow</a
    >{" "}with{" "}
    <a
      class="text-text-700 font-medium underline hover:text-froly-500 transition-all duration-200 hover:no-underline underline-offset-2"
      href="https://benreinhart.com">Ben Reinhart</a
    >.
  </p>
  <p class="max-w-xl pt-8 sm:pt-6">
    I recently was a founding engineer at{" "}
    <a
      class="text-text-700 font-medium underline hover:text-froly-500 transition-all duration-200 hover:no-underline underline-offset-2"
      href="https://privy.io">Privy</a
    >. Before that I spent 4 years on the ML platform team at{" "}
    <a
      class="text-text-700 font-medium underline hover:text-froly-500 transition-all duration-200 hover:no-underline underline-offset-2"
      href="https://getcruise.com">Cruise</a
    >, 2 years at {" "}
    <a
      class="text-text-700 font-medium underline hover:text-froly-500 transition-all duration-200 hover:no-underline underline-offset-2"
      href="https://pinterest.com">Pinterest</a
    >{" "}
    building real-time ML systems, and a few years working full-stack at lesser-known
    startups.
  </p>
  <p class="max-w-xl pt-8 sm:pt-6">
    I live in California and grew up in France, where I got my engineering
    Masters from{" "}
    <a
      class="text-text-700 font-medium underline hover:text-froly-500 transition-all duration-200 hover:no-underline underline-offset-2"
      href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mines_Paris_%E2%80%93_PSL"
      >Mines Paris</a
    >.
  </p>
  <div class="pt-8 flex items-center justify-center gap-10">
    <a
      class="text-text-700 text-xl font-medium underline hover:text-froly-500 transition-all duration-200 hover:no-underline underline-offset-2"
      href="/blog"
      class="text-xl"
    >
      Blog
    </a>
    <a
      class="text-text-700 text-xl font-medium underline hover:text-froly-500 transition-all duration-200 hover:no-underline underline-offset-2"
      href="/projects"
      class="text-xl"
    >
      Projects
    </a>
    <a
      class="text-text-700 text-xl font-medium underline hover:text-froly-500 transition-all duration-200 hover:no-underline underline-offset-2"
      href="/quotes"
      class="text-xl"
    >
      Favorite quotes
    </a>
  </div>
</Layout>
